original_title:
I think this moment was far more important than we realize.

While Trump has NATO leaders and Zelensky in a photo op, he directs their attention to a painting from that day in Butler.

And all the leaders look like they just saw a ghost.  — The Donald
article_summary: Trump's photo op with NATO leaders and Zelensky at a painting in Butler sparks speculation about a potential revelation regarding an attempt on his life. Users on the post discuss accountability for the incident and express support for Trump's alleged knowledge of those involved.</s>
